# How to enable an instance of Exim to run on different ports (26 or 587)

In order to enable an instance of Exim to run on a different port, such as 26 or 587, please do the following steps:

1) Log on to your WHM as root.

2) Go to "**Service Configuration**" section and click on "**Service Manager**" icon.

```diagram

```

3) Enable the instance of Exim here shown as below:

```diagram

```

4) Then click on "**Save**".
